fields.title: Master 108 Surya Namaskars
fields.description: Complete 108 Surya Namaskars (Sun Salutations) in one session. A traditional yoga challenge that tests endurance and devotion!

fields.title: Learn a Classical Indian Raga
fields.description: Learn to sing or play a classical Indian raga you've never performed before. Share a recording of your performance.

fields.title: Feed 50 Street Animals
fields.description: Prepare food and feed 50 street dogs or cats in your area. Document this act of compassion and share the experience.

fields.title: Cook Authentic Biryani from Scratch
fields.description: Master the art of making authentic Hyderabadi or Lucknowi biryani from scratch. Share the cooking process and final result!

fields.title: Complete a 10K Morning Run
fields.description: Wake up at 5 AM and complete a 10K run before sunrise. Capture the beautiful morning views and your achievement!

fields.title: Create Rangoli Art
fields.description: Design and create a beautiful rangoli pattern using traditional or modern techniques. Share your colorful creation!

fields.title: Learn Sanskrit Shlokas
fields.description: Memorize and recite 5 Sanskrit shlokas with proper pronunciation. Share a video of your recitation.

fields.title: Build an Indian Language App
fields.description: Create a simple mobile or web app that teaches basic words in any Indian regional language.

fields.title: Visit 5 Historical Monuments
fields.description: Explore 5 historical monuments in your city or nearby areas. Document their history and significance.

fields.title: Master 50 Bhangra Moves
fields.description: Learn and perform 50 different Bhangra dance moves. Create an energetic dance video showcasing your skills!
